OL,3,CAfghanistan's exiled female cricketers
OL,4,Cfind a way back to the international
OL,5,Cgame
OL,7,FFor the first time in more than three
OL,8,Fyears, Benafsha Hasmiri has played
OL,9,Fcricket for Afghanistan, but it wasn't
OL,10,Fan official match, and it wasn't
OL,11,Fstaged in the country where she is
OL,12,Ffrom.
OL,14,FInstead, a team made up of exiles like
OL,15,Fher turned out against a Cricket
OL,16,FWithout Borders XI in a symbolic
OL,17,Fmeeting on Thursday in Melbourne,
OL,18,Fwhere many of the Afghan women are now
OL,19,Frefugees.
