OL,7,FHasmiri, who in 2021 was a contracted
OL,8,Finternational cricketer, was one of
OL,9,Fmore than 100 women who were evacuated
OL,10,Ffrom their homeland as the Taliban
OL,11,Ftook back control.
OL,13,F"It was like a bad wind coming through
OL,14,Four life, destroying everything. It
OL,15,Fhappened really quick," she told ITV
OL,16,FNews.
OL,18,F'We didn't lose our identity,' says
OL,19,FBenafsha Hasmiri
