OL,7,FWomen's sport was one of the first
OL,8,Ffreedoms the new hardline government
OL,9,Fdismantled.
OL,11,FSince then, the restrictions have
OL,12,Fintensified with high school and
OL,13,Funiversity now banned for women, as is
OL,14,Fspeaking in public, showing your face
OL,15,Foutside the home, driving, smartphones
OL,16,Fand using parks and gyms.
OL,18,FThere are many other areas of life
OL,19,Fthat much of the rest of the world
OL,20,Ftakes for granted which are also now
OL,21,Fout of reach for Afghan women.
