OL,7,FThursday's match was played at the
OL,8,Fstart of the women's Ashes Test match
OL,9,Fbetween Australia and England.
OL,11,FEngland's captain Heather Knight told
OL,12,Fa press conference the exhibition
OL,13,Fmatch was a "special" fixture.
OL,15,F"The fact that they're playing is a
OL,16,Fmassive, good feeling story; obviously
OL,17,Fwhat's going on in their country, and
OL,18,Fthe hard situations those girls have
OL,19,Fgone through, just meeting them there,
OL,20,Fit's super inspirational," she said.
