OL,7,FAll this comes as more than 150 MPs
OL,8,Fhave signed a letter pressuring
OL,9,FEngland's men's team to consider
OL,10,Fboycotting their upcoming match with
OL,11,FAfghanistan.
OL,13,FThey want to put pressure on the
OL,14,FInternational Cricket Council (ICC)
OL,15,Fwho have been relatively quiet on the
OL,16,Ffate of the Afghan women.
OL,18,FLeading the campaign is the Labour MP
OL,19,FTonia Antoniazzi, who told ITV News
OL,20,Fshe hadn't received a reply from the
OL,21,FICC, weeks after sending the letter.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G6/12
