OL,7,F"I think that is unacceptable, I can
OL,8,Faccept that there isn't going to be a
OL,9,Fboycott, but what are they doing, they
OL,10,Fgo the Afghan men's team #17m and yet
OL,11,FAfghan women cricketers live in exile
OL,12,Fin Australia, and they don't see any
OL,13,Fof that money."
