OL,7,FAntoniazzi said she'd had positive
OL,8,Fmeetings with Richard Gould, the
OL,9,FEngland and Wales Cricket Board (ECB)
OL,10,Fchief executive, and praised the prime
OL,11,Fminister for calling on the ICC to
OL,12,F"deliver on their own rules", which
OL,13,Frequire all Test-playing nations to
OL,14,Fhave a national women's team.
OL,16,FBut the Labour backbencher called on
OL,17,Fthe government and the ECB to go
OL,18,Ffurther: "I think we do need to have a
OL,19,Fbit more backbone, to be honest with
OL,20,Fyou," she said.
