OL,7,F''I do think the ECB does. I was
OL,8,Freally pleased with my meeting, but
OL,9,Fthere is more we can do. And in the
OL,10,Frun-up to the tournament, this is what
OL,11,Fwe need to be doing, the government
OL,12,Fneeds to speak out, so does the ECB,
OL,13,Fand the ICC needs to put things in
OL,14,Fplace to support the Afghan women's
OL,15,Fcricket team.''
OL,17,F'The boycott is not the right answer'
