OL,7,FWhile Hasmiri and her teammates are
OL,8,Fgrateful for the MP's show of
OL,9,Fsolidarity, most of them do not
OL,10,Fbelieve such extreme action will help.
OL,12,F"The boycott is not the right answer,
OL,13,Fbecause I don't want to be selfish
OL,14,Flike the (the men's team)," she told
OL,15,FITV News.
OL,17,F"They're not supporting us, they're
OL,18,Fjust trying to ignore us, so I want
OL,19,Fthem to play and go further.
