OL,7,F"They are representing our country, it
OL,8,Fmakes me think about our country, not
OL,9,Fjust me and my team, a boycott won't
OL,10,Fbe the right answer."
OL,12,F"Afghanistan people do nothing to earn
OL,13,Fmoney," she added.
OL,15,F"Cricket can be the only financial
OL,16,Fanswer for some people in Afghanistan,
OL,17,Fso if we cut them off, many people
OL,18,Fwill really find earning money, having
OL,19,Ffood, giving food to their children,
OL,20,Fit will make that really hard."
